<div style="background-color: #FFFFFF;  border-radius: 20px 20px 20px 20px; color: #000000; width: 90%; margin-left: 0%; margin-right: 0%; padding: 5px 5px 0px 5px;">

<p style="color: black; line-height: 1.25; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; font-size: 18px"><b>If you are not already a verified teacher,</b></p>
<p style="color: black; line-height: 1.25; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 0px; font-size: 18px"> <a href="https://form.jotform.com/240863841362155" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" >Click here</a> to complete the form to become a verified teacher. 
</p>

___

#### **Note:** We try to process requests for teacher verification as fast as we can but because it is a manual process, it can take up to 7 business days to complete. <a href="https://support.code.org/hc/en-us/articles/115001550131-How-to-Become-a-Verified-Teacher" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" >Click here</a> for more information, including a list of frequently asked questions.



